      • propertyJsonReader

        public void propertyJsonReader(java.lang.String path)
        This method is filling the property array list in the game by reading the json file for properties.
        Parameters:
        path - This method takes a file path as parameter
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - If the file doesn't exist or it can't be founded method throws a file exception to warn us
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - If there is no such a file
        org.json.simple.parser.ParseException - If json object is not be able to be parsed.
        Since:
        2016.04.12
